⸻

LAYOUT PRINCIPLES

Maximum Width

Content should breathe.

Recommended:

* max-width: 1280px
* content width: 720–900px

Never stretch text too wide.

⸻

Spacing

Large vertical spacing.

The product should feel calm and breathable.

Use generous:

* section padding
* whitespace
* margin spacing

Avoid compressed fintech layouts.

⸻

Grid

Use asymmetrical editorial layouts.

Avoid:

* perfect centered SaaS boxes everywhere
* rigid startup templates

Instead:

* cinematic compositions
* offset content
* oversized imagery
* layered depth

